<section id="post-product">
  <h3><span class="post-method">POST</span> - Añadir Producto</h3>
  <p>Añade un nuevo producto a la base de datos. Esta consulta verifica el cuerpo de la solicitud para evitar recibir datos incorrectos o vacíos.</p>

  <h4>Ejemplo solicitud correcta</h4>
  <pre>
    <span class="type-request">HTTP</span>

    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">POST https://fake-store-alpha.vercel.app/api/products HTTP/1.1</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">Content-Length: 86</span>
    
    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">&lbrace;</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 20px;">"name": "smartphone",</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 20px;">"description": "samsung smartphone",</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 20px;">"price": 124.32,</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 20px;">"categoryId": 1 // Id de la categoría a la que pertenece el producto</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">&rbrace;</span>

  </pre>
  
  <h4>201 - Created</h4>
  <pre>
    <span class="type-request">HTTP</span>
    
    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">HTTP/1.1 201 Created</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">Location: http://fake-store-alpha.vercel.app/api/products/&lt;--ID--&gt;</span>

    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">&lbrace;</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 20px;">"id": &lt;--ID--&gt;,</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 20px;">"name": "smartphone",</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 20px;">"description": "samsung smartphone",</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 20px;">"price": 124.32,</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 20px;">"categoryId: 1,</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 20px;">"paths": &lbrack;</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">&lbrace;</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"ref": "self",</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"href": "/api/products/&lt;--ID--&gt;",</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"action": "GET"</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">&rbrace;,</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">&lbrace;</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"ref": "self",</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"href": "/api/products/&lt;--ID--&gt;",</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"action": "PUT"</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">&rbrace;,</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">&lbrace;</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"ref": "self",</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"href": "/api/products/&lt;--ID--&gt;",</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"action": "DELETE"</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">&rbrace;,</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">&lbrace;</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"ref": "categories",</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"href": "/api/categories/1",</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"action": "GET"</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">&rbrace;,</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">&lbrace;</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"ref": "categories",</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"href": "/api/categories/1",</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"action": "PUT"</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">&rbrace;,</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">&lbrace;</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"ref": "categories",</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"href": "/api/categories/1",</span>
        <span style="padding-left: 40px;">"action": "DELETE"</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">&rbrace;</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 20px;">&rbrack;</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">&rbrace;</span>

  </pre>

  <hr />

  <h4>Ejemplo solicitud incorrecta</h4>
  <pre>
    <span class="type-request">HTTP</span>

    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">POST https://fake-store-alpha.vercel.app/api/products HTTP/1.1</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8</span>

  </pre>
  
  <h4>400 - Bad Request</h4>
  <em>Si no se proporcionan en el cuerpo de la solicitud los datos necesarios para crear un producto, responderá con un error</em>
  <pre>
    <span class="type-request">HTTP</span>
    
    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8</span>

    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">&lbrace;</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 20px;">"message": "Error verifying the data required to create a new product",</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 20px;">"status": 400,</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 20px;">"errors": &lbrack;</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">"The value of the 'name' property is required",</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">"The value of the 'description' property is required",</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">"The value of the 'price' property is required",</span>
      <span style="padding-left: 30px;">"The value of the 'categoryId' property is required",</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 20px;">&rbrack;</span>
    <span style="padding-left: 10px;">&rbrace;</span>

  </pre>
</section>
